In Africa there are different religions as well as various cultures and cultural foods. For this reason there are some places in Africa that consumer needs that are not really popular in other African places.
It is believed that the consumption of dog meat in certain African countries might have benefits to the individuals consuming the meat.
These benefits include:
1. Increases stamina
It is believed that the consumption of dog meat increases stamina especially in men. This has not been scientifically proven but will centuries people have consumed dogmeat because of these beliefs.
2. Can protect you from sicknesses
The consumption of dog meat is also believed to have properties that can protect individuals from sicknesses.
3. It is a delicacy
Dark meat is a delicacy in some parts of the world and it is believed that consuming it might have spiritual effects. In some parts of the world it is believed that dog meat is only consumed by individuals of a high calibre.


